<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />When I remained silent, my bones were wasting away</para>

<para style="q1">while I groaned all day long.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />For day and night your hand was heavy upon me.</para>

<para style="q1">My strength withered as in summer drought.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>
